{"tid":1522555,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[救你一命post] 所有係西環玩緊捉迷藏嘅人入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-31T13:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T13:43:23.000Z","uid":286552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d69959c67505ac26ef40344728eadd0ec1862ed3","tid":1522555,"uid":286552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"記得跑快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[member] 我之前係嗰邊返咗一段短時間嘅工，我依家諗返起就發現係堅尼地城有個位幾啱人入捉依因，嗰到就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">堅尼地城社區綜合大樓</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6whRygT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6whRygT.png&h=510e0808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我點解會話佢ok呢，首先你望一望地圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wSJma38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwSJma38.png&h=2d64a1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後你再望下呢張地圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Qp4ThF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Qp4ThF.jpg&h=525a4ccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紫色圈圈係社區會堂<br />\n<br />\n我相信大家都望到佢嘅地理位置係唔差，咁你又會問啦，社區會堂又如何，遲早會關門。其實無錯，佢一到夜晚9點幾10點就會關門，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但係假設你入到去嘅話，佢一樓同二樓個廁所係可以由入，因為佢上面係有商戶係上面做嘢，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而你係可以選擇隨時走</span></span></span>。雖然係廁所過一段時間係唔舒服㗎啦，但點都好過去臭格先。<br />\n<br />\n咁假如入唔到去咁點算先，咁你就望下大門隔離個小門<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23RShO5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23RShO5.png&h=e70217c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeAGVAP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeAGVAP.png&h=4ff1d1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢呢個係可以上去樓上個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">停車場</span></span>，而社會會堂嘅人都係可以透過呢到走，我無記錯嘅話佢嘅停車場都有好多層下，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要揾位玩捉依因都咪話唔差</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係大家假設想入去嘅話，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得換裝</span></span>，入面有cctv係基本嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後祝咁多位香港人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武運亨通</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQu1bbv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQu1bbv.jpg&h=17961170&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}